<div class="title">Too Strong</div>
<div class="substance">Blue Lotus & Alcohol</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Sha&Exact=1">Sha</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Sha. "Too Strong: An Experience with Blue Lotus & Alcohol (exp42685)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Oct 17, 2009. erowid.org/exp/42685</div>

<br/>



